p.n: Block Rocker Explorer Sound System w/ Bluetooth (Various Colors)
p.sd:
• Stream music wirelessly from any Bluetooth device up to 100 feet away
  • Works w/ iPad, iPhone, Android, more
  • Digital AM/FM radio w/ durable antenna
  • Built-in rechargeable battery lasts up to 50 hrs
  • Recessed wheels and telescoping handle for portability
  • Easy Pair links your NFC-enabled smartphone or tablet with a simple tap
p.ld:
Blast music wirelessly from smartphones, tablets, and more.

Crank up your music whenever and wherever you want: Explorer Bluetooth is a powerful and flexible all-in-one sound system for mobile devices, MP3 players, microphones, and instruments. Explorer Bluetooth's wireless capability means you can keep your iPad, iPhone, Android or other Bluetooth music device right by your side as you blast your music. NFC-enabled smartphones or tablets can connect with just a simple tap using the Easy Pair feature.

You can even listen to your favorite radio station or to the big game—just dial it in on Explorer Bluetooth’s built-in AM/FM radio. The radio includes six presets so you can store your favorite radio stations. You can also plug in and crank up instruments, microphones and more. A high-quality microphone is included.

With its built-in battery and charge indicator, Explorer Bluetooth lets you enjoy your music anywhere—indoors or outside—all day. A power cord is also included for nonstop music. You get powerful sound that's perfect for parties, BBQs, drive-in movies, family get-togethers, and more.

p.sd:
Free standard shipping for online orders.

808 CANZ wireless Bluetooth speakers provide big sound in a little package, featuring a rechargeable lithium polymer battery for 6 hours of playtime at normal volume from a single charge.
p.ld: It's pretty simple. 808 is all about street smarts, cutting-edge audio technology, and intelligently priced products for the discerning enthusiast. Our goal is to make gear that works as well as it looks. We set out to make stuff that we'd want to use ourselves. No hype. No silly celebrity endorsements. If it says "808" on it, you can trust that it will not only enhance your listening experience – it will let you hear your music like never before.

p.n: Braven 705 Portable Wireless Speaker - Various Colors
p.sd: Precision engineered with a shock-absorbent thermoplastic exterior and sleek finish, the Braven 705 Speaker is offered in a wide variety of colors to match your personal style.
p.ld: Lightweight portability meets big sound with the powerful Braven 705 Speaker. Custom high-fidelity audio drivers deliver room-filling sound to your music, media, conference calls and more. For a powerful, immersive left and right stereo experience, pair any two Braven 7-Series speakers together using Braven's highly-acclaimed TrueWireless™ Technology. Precision engineered with a shock-absorbent thermoplastic exterior and sleek finish, the Braven 705 Speaker is offered in a wide variety of colors to match your personal style.

p.sd:
• 3-way speakers with 270-degree sound
  • Two 2.5" side firing tweeters
  • One 3" front firing full range speaker
  • Two 3" side firing passive radiators
  • 20 watts of high fidelity sound
  • Class-D Amplification for best performance
  • Built-in rechargeable battery supports up to 8 hours of music
p.ld: The Monster Tower of Music Speaker delivers your digital music with clarity, power and expandability. Our 3 speaker drivers and 2 passive radiators deliver a high lever clarity and range. With 20W of power, the audiophone will appreciate robust sound. With EZPLAY, you can expand up to 8 total speakers and listen to music all around you (additional speaker purchase required).

p.whyweloveit: People just can't stop saying enough good things about the iHome iBT30 Bluetooth® Speaker System. It's super compact—perfect when you're short on space—but has the sound of a full-rack stereo system with plenty of treble and bass. Charging is quick and incredibly easy with the nearly invisible base. But best of all, it works with virtually any Bluetooth-enabled device for true wireless portability that allows you to groove on the move.
p.sd:
• Wirelessly stream music from iPad, iPhone, iPod touch, Android, Blackberry and other Bluetooth-enabled devices
  • USB port to charge mobile devices (charging cable not included)
  • Internal rechargeable Lithium-ion battery (charging base included
  •  Reson8 speaker chamber technology and SRS TruBass for superior sound
  • Aux-in jack to play audio from audio devices equipped with 3.5mm headphone jack (audio connection cable included)
  • 100V - 240V universal voltage AC adaptor
p.ld:
The iHome iBT30 Bluetooth Speaker System is a compact wireless speaker with a rechargeable lithium-ion battery that delivers big sound and is truly wireless. Features Bluetooth audio and stereo aware pairing to enable wireless stereo sound when linked with another compatible iHome speaker. The USB charging port allows the user to continue to list to their music while charging their device.

p.n: Altec Lansing Boom Jacket Speaker - Various Colors
p.sd:
• Waterproof, sandproof, shockproof and snowproof construction
  • Floatable and submersible
  • 40 hour battery life
p.ld: You live life to the fullest and you need a Bluetooth speaker that lives up to that same demand. The Boom Jacket has you covered. The IP67 rating means that it can go underwater up to 3’ for 30 minutes. Plus, it floats! Rock the days and nights away with 40 hours of battery life and the ability to recharge your smartphone or other portable devices. The Boom Jacket is so high tech, it not only talks to you (spoken caller ID and battery level)  - but it also reacts to voice commands to answer or reject phone calls. Ultra-versatile with its mounting bracke,t you can secure the Boom Jacket wherever you want. The Aux In port lets you rock your tunes from any mobile music device with a headphone jack.
